                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The anguished flame compels the prayers of a creature they can see within 60 feet, and that creature must attempt a @Check[will|dc:41|traits:emotion,mental] save. A creature with the holy trait gets a degree of success one better than their result.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature uses its reaction to pray.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature prays. It is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} and can't use reactions for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 2}.</p>"
