                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The anguished hellfire's solar flare aura is active</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The anguished hellfire fixes their fiery eyes on a creature they can see within 30 feet. The target must immediately attempt a Fortitude save against the anguished hellfire's solar flare. If the creature was already @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Dazzled] by solar flare before attempting its save, a failed save causes it to become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] until the end of its next turn.</p>"
